article_title: Spelling bee winner, contestants reap rewards
article_text:
Kankakee, IL (60901)

Today

Sun and clouds mixed. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 86F. Winds SSW at 10 to 20 mph..

Tonight

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms overnight. Low 61F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 40%.
